Package: spicy
Title: Data Management and Variable Exploration
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Amal", "Tawfik", , "amal.tawfik@hesav.ch", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-2422-1555"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive summary of the variables in a data frame. Extract essential metadata, including variable names, labels, values, classes, the number of distinct values, the number of valid (non-missing) observations, and the number of missing values. Quickly assess the structure and content of a data frame.
